Plot: Balikoowa in the City follows a story of "Balikoowa" (Housen Mushema), a villager who heads to the city (Kampala) on an errand to his aunt's daughter "Sophia" (Marion Asiro). He has to deal with the city life for as long his errand lasts.
Title: Balikoowa in the City
Actors: Mwanje Allan, Marion Asiro, Mushema Housen, Jay K. Mulungi
